show.description:
A billionaire’s surprise gift—a law firm for his wife—shocks everyone. Amid corporate politics, manipulation, and betrayal, she fights to protect her dignity and rise above the chaos.
As hidden truths emerge, a battle for respect, redemption, and second chances begins.
